/*
Hard/Lunatic trainer overrides.

This file uses the same trainer syntax as src/data/trainers.party.
Entries here default to Difficulty: Hard, so a trainer only needs the
same identifier to override the Normal party when the current difficulty
is DIFFICULTY_HARD or DIFFICULTY_LUNATIC.

If a trainer is not listed here, the game falls back to src/data/trainers.party.

Example:

=== TRAINER_OLIVIA ===
Name: OLIVIA
Class: Beauty
Pic: Beauty
Gender: Female
Music: Female
Double Battle: No
AI: Check Bad Move

Clamperl
Level: 40
- Water Pulse
- Rain Dance
- Whirlpool
- Iron Defense
*/

